loriously has 10 preset cooking functions, an easy-to-use design and included accessories: a rotisserie shaft, a roasting basket and removal tools, among others. Crownful is also one of our favorite brands for mini fridges and, with its 50s-eqsue makeup, it would look amazing with the Smeg’s Coffee Grinder ($330). Check out the New York Post Shopping section for more content.